"A.P.238/4/8": "Come to think of it, that ARKS Battle Championship that Huey was talking about is coming up."

"I guess it's about testing our ability to work as a team."
"Well, that's reasonable. Fighting in a party is the essence of how ARKS operate."
"Oh, if you haven't decided on someone yet, why not join me?"
"If you're alright with that, call me on the day when you're ready to go."
